  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist Epic Auto Towers, a game from our son, a professional game developer!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The third part of the puzzle-platformer game Butterfly - Funny Twins! <br>Enjoy the new 40 levels of original design! Your logical and platformer skills are required!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You control two caterpillars at the same time;<br></li><li>The caterpillars can’t jump on their own - find a way to complete platformer levels!<br></li><li>Bounce off the enemies to your advantage!<br></li><li>Use pipes – while one caterpillar is in the pipe, the other can move in either direction!<br></li><li>Put one caterpillar in a secluded place so the other still free to go!<br></li><li>Manage this active team of twins tied by your fingers!<br></li><li>Platform skills are useful, but try to find a simple logical solution!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1356300/extras/455cbb64c6d4b7e583d63b62fac8eaac.poster.avif?t=1695519151\" width=280 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1356300/extras/455cbb64c6d4b7e583d63b62fac8eaac.webm?t=1695519151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1356300/extras/455cbb64c6d4b7e583d63b62fac8eaac.mp4?t=1695519151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><br>And check if you missed the first and second parts:<br><br><br>",
